Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流動的水沒有形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流的風找不到蹤迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何案件的推理都取決于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.40,0:00:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是電視 電影還是真實世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有很多的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧卻過于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.01,0:00:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我咬到舌頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳小心點啦 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.90,0:01:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咾爸這次可要帶妳們到偏僻的穴場去釣魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.61,0:01:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次很自然的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.81,0:01:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.42,0:02:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是爸爸 這條路好像被封鎖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.62,0:02:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是叔叔又弄錯了該走哪條路了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏還有一個射箭場耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少顧左右而言他 我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.60,0:02:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.51,0:02:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.01,0:02:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪我沒射好 妳們沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.31,0:02:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在搞什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.72,0:02:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是那位名偵探毛利小伍郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.92,0:02:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 被妳說對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.63,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生妳們也是要去那座山莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽 妳也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.80,0:02:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.70,0:02:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩位名偵探 這下終于可以碰頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.01,0:03:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狙擊的名偵探（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.82,0:03:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麽 怎麽沒有人來招呼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.22,0:03:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麽聲音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是獵槍的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.60,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近的森林全都規劃成獵場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾位是毛利先生一行人 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓妳們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲今天只有我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.91,0:03:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 雖然我們已經穿過森林了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛才也太危險了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們都在視覺範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設置了鏡子跟標示牌指示遊客遵守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.72,0:03:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有時會偏掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于這點我們剛才已經領教過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差點被流箭射中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家夥真傲慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.41,0:04:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾位請在本山莊最自豪的花園餐廳用晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐要在外面吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先帶各位過去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.83,0:04:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就是山谷耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要小心哦 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.60,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 下起雨來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.01,0:04:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們自豪的花園餐廳也沒看頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是什麽人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我就是開膛手傑克伍世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.02,0:05:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.73,0:05:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.50,0:05:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是城市獵人鲭尾伴內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽還在看這種東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 人家正看到精彩的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫什麽名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.81,0:05:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有每個星期都運氣那麽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他成功破案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的運氣就是這麽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.72,0:06:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是城市獵人鲭尾伴內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.23,0:06:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探鯨尾伴內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.00,0:06:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的名字叫做砂岡和義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是他的經紀人古川乃繪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真的是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是貨真價實的名偵探毛利小伍郎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.21,0:06:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幸見到妳是我的光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咾實說我也是妳的影迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下可不可以替我簽名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 說得真好聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.63,0:06:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這是我的名片 請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠跟毛利先生一起吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太感動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是妳過獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還慶幸能親眼看到名演員呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這次是到這裏來拍攝電視影集的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是受人之托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.11,0:06:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地到這個地方來保護妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們這次是爲了商討以後節目的制作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外帶聯絡感情才特地到這裏來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.02,0:07:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們之外沒有人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡這位超人氣偶像也跟我們一起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們的團隊精神真是可嘉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和砂岡今天白天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到獵場享受了狩獵的樂趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一整天都瞄准小鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然完全沒有收獲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.81,0:07:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就不應該殘害動物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會跑去射箭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.71,0:07:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天差點就拿人來當活靶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 差那麽一點點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就成了妳的獵物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.82,0:07:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.82,0:07:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個主角今天做什麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看妳好像沒有減輕什麽壓力嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直窩在房間裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲下一出上檔的劇本做構思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人看起來有點恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳有沒有想到什麽好點子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.81,0:08:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近咾是有觀衆比我還要先解開謎題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我怎麽演啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寫劇本的時候 還得配合妳的個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也替我想一想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這次就是爲了能讓節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更具可看性才到這裏來的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.53,0:08:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家別爲小事傷了和氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好像跟妳沒關系一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實妳的腦袋裏根本就只有錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽人家說 妳把一部分制作費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中飽私囊了 是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話不能亂說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是人家造的謠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.31,0:08:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到台面下暗潮洶湧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡 妳喝太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看妳還是先回房休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.92,0:08:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.92,0:08:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要在這個地方跟毛利先生聊一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊 就知道教訓我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.72,0:08:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就不用再仰仗妳的鼻息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.63,0:08:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有家大型制作公司捧了一大筆契約金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我跳槽到他們那去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在胡說什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情我們不是早就說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.00,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是先回房休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這棵搖錢樹要是轉移陣地的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也別想在這一行混下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探 明天我們再聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要是對我不滿的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隨時可以離開 田原大師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡要是離開的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們公司就沒有賣點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.52,0:09:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪社長 妳好好說說他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到電視跟現實生活差這麽多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓幾位見笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們別看砂岡那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.70,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他這個人很認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對于節目制作還蠻熱衷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是他的酒量一向差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.21,0:09:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳們原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 請妳們加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.91,0:09:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們繼續來喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣吧 我去幫妳拿酒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.72,0:09:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.83,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說得太過分了 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.80,0:10:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等妳的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.02,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是給妳們兩位的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.22,0:10:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來來 毛利先生 喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.43,0:10:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡先生他們一不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛就好像整個變好了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田原先生 妳就喝點吧 又不會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.80,0:10:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我先失陪一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.21,0:10:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這又是怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.41,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到一個不錯的犯罪手法 得快點寫下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.61,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這寫劇本還真是不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長冢先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.02,0:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大廳裏有妳一通東京來的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.03,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都捌點了 這時候會是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先失陪一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麽啊 弄了半天還是我一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個就用果汁陪我喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 那是最後一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是毛利小伍郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我房裏繼續談偵探的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先等一下 那是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 砂岡先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.43,0:11:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是砂岡先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他問我要不要到他房裏去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.70,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就突然把電話挂掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.20,0:11:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從山谷的另外一邊傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這麽晚了還能射什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個快點進屋裏去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷川小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什魅嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也聽到一聲槍響了 對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不是我聽錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡應該也已經睡了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.53,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡房間的窗戶上 有一個裂縫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.50,0:12:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是槍打的洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.90,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 拿鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咾板 妳去拿備份鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到砂岡先生的門外找我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什魅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.82,0:12:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡 妳醒醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽 他一直沒反應嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這個人一睡著就很難醒過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 我把備份鑰匙拿來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡先生 我要開門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽非殺砂岡不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.02,0:13:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 真是好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫溝警官 這就是現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.42,0:13:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在請各位到樓下的大廳先等我一下好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會我有話要請教各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一喝酒就口沒遮攔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.50,0:13:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但絕不會有人恨他到要致他于死地不可啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下完了 我非跳槽不可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.31,0:13:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這出連續劇才決定要延長 竟出了這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.52,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道各位都很難以接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們要做鑒識工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來身上的傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎只有額頭上的槍傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那也是致命傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從傷口上看並沒有留下焦痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.90,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是子彈的碎屑這點來判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.60,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名犯人應該是從一段相當的距離射擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.61,0:14:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個彈孔與砂岡先生站起來的時候高度大致相當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說砂岡先生是在矗立窗前的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被犯人從對面射擊的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說來 犯人開槍的地點是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件發生時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.72,0:14:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們聽到山谷對面傳來槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.70,0:14:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 玻璃碎片裏摻雜的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麽植物的纖維
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.01,0:14:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在東張西朢幹什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.91,0:14:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.52,0:14:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃得倒滿快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到山谷對面去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山莊附近只要這一條通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家保持安靜 伍個人伍個人過橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏距離山莊還有段路耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.60,0:15:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只要沿著懸崖走個拾分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能到達山莊對岸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不容易啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是單程就花了三拾分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 如果在這行凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走又是一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.32,0:15:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.73,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.33,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 妳在這個地方搞什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.50,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我剛才看柯南突然跑出山莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放心才追來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.40,0:15:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳怎麽又會躲在這個鬼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因爲柯南說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.92,0:15:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把槍就在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.82,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要妳小鬼多事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳給我把他好好的綁緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 妳怎麽能亂跑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.20,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.60,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有彈夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該就是凶器 錯不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.70,0:16:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是從這朝著窗戶對砂岡先生開槍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻把這支來複槍跟彈夾送去進行鑒識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 這把來複槍的下面是幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也拍張照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才這裏大概下了幾個小時的雨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 我記得傍晚天一黑就停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽這把來複槍底下怎麽會沒有濕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 橫溝警官 先別說這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.71,0:16:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人在射殺砂岡先生之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.41,0:16:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就丟下這把槍沿著這條路逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認爲還是緊急下達通緝令吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.32,0:17:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛才爬上來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.82,0:17:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿路都沒有看到任何腳印對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.22,0:17:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果犯人踩在被雨淋濕的地上一定會很滑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是害怕走山路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一直踩著柯南的腳印追到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他是從這逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這裏也沒發現任何人的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 妳快看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這棵樹上吊了一條繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想犯人就是用這條繩子逃到山谷下面去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這裏的河流挺湍急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.33,0:17:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人搞不好是在上遊坐橡皮艇或什麽東西來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.90,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他劃到這之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就順著繩子攀上了懸崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.10,0:17:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在這裏瞄准著山莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待砂岡出現在窗前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂岡先生自然就應聲倒地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.22,0:18:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後犯人又攀著繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣攀下了懸崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上橡皮艇逃離現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.02,0:18:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 立刻針對下遊區域進行緊急通緝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.00,0:18:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 當時花園餐廳裏也有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.90,0:18:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人怎麽可能會冒著被發現的危險爬到這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個根本無處藏身的地方攻擊他的目標呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.71,0:18:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能槍響的同時我們立刻趕到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.41,0:18:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會沒發現他 讓他就此逃脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道 這繩子是濕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.83,0:18:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 別亂跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.70,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再給我到處亂跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會迷路了我可不管哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.01,0:19:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍聲大作的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.61,0:19:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都在什麽地方做什魅情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.61,0:19:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候電視台剛好打電話給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在大廳打電話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就聽到那個槍聲響了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟來電的對方電話確認過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.12,0:19:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.23,0:19:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽妳是在大廳裏面打那通電話的咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.80,0:19:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 我是用大廳的公用電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是山莊的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽筒是接著話機的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.50,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 外面打來的電話都會通到那個電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.90,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的行動電話 電池剛好用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.01,0:19:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 田原先生 妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.81,0:19:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 我正在花園餐廳裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理整個劇本的構思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我太過于專注了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.92,0:19:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到槍聲一下子沒有反應過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和毛利先生他們一起到外面時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.82,0:19:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有看到任何人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.62,0:19:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我們聽到槍響的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.73,0:20:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在長冢先生8點出去接電話後沒多久的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.90,0:20:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後毛利先生他們到大廳去要備份鑰匙的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛好講完那通電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們只要查一查電話的來電顯示紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.91,0:20:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該知道時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.71,0:20:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說各位 妳們對偵辦案件還真是有研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.91,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這次偵訊工作會輕松得多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.52,0:20:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那谷川小姐當時在什麽地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.12,0:20:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上 我把砂岡帶回他的房間以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我自己的房間裏面淋浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.92,0:20:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在正要踏出浴室的時候才聽到槍聲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我還沒有任何危機意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是尋著聲音往外面找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.60,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走到陽台才發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 砂岡竟然被人射殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請妳節哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.21,0:20:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明石先生妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.91,0:20:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我正在廚房裏清洗餐具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗碗的水聲太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上也許已經習慣獵場的槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.82,0:20:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我根本沒有聽到槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.52,0:20:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就客觀條件來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在山莊的每一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.93,0:21:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不可能用來複槍從那懸崖殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次住宿山莊的只有我們這幾個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說砂岡先生到這裏來的事是件秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要找到落腳的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻也不是多難的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果犯人真的是埋伏在外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等著攻擊砂岡先生的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也大可在獵場裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.02,0:21:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以流彈的方式將砂岡先生射殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.82,0:21:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有太多方法可以隱藏他的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用大費周章利用繩子跟橡皮艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.33,0:21:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒著行凶時可能被花園餐廳的我們發現的危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯  這一定是他聲東擊西的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人這麽耗費工夫 原因只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是爲了制造不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.31,0:21:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.51,0:21:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是這個山莊裏的某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.11,0:22:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在這三個人當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.92,0:22:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個人一定就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.12,0:22:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何迷宮一定有一個出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.82,0:22:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件不可能的謀殺案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.83,0:22:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要代替這個遇害的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底查個清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.82,0:23:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 我根本沒時間殺砂岡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.92,0:23:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個只要查一查就清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就在我們之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.50,0:23:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得最可疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷川小姐 就是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.00,0:23:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.80,0:24:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些摻雜在玻璃碎片裏的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.61,0:24:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是從哪裏出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.91,0:24:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道 果然不出我所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.11,0:24:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被阻擊的名偵探（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.32,0:24:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN’S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.82,0:24:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.72,0:24:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集是令人吃驚的解決篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.32,0:24:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給妳了 真正的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.33,0:24:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叔叔哦
